						<div class="postbody">What are you doing computation wise for DCP? My CPU passes all of the nestest.nes illegal ops. For DCP I just do a DEC followed by a CMP operation, then move to the next instruction. That's where DCP gets it's mnemonic. It's a concatenation of the two.</div>

